channel.description: This noob got onto my server, and he became a admin... i dunno how, Then he banned my Owner Acc. Anyone tell me how to unban me.

item.title: Ffs, need help, i been banned on my own server lmao
item.dc:creator: @yppman yppman
item.description:
@yppman wrote:

… Okay first go to your server folder, like the one with your runserver.bat, compile.bat, etc. When you’re there go to the folder data. You’ll see a few text files. Double click on bannedusers.txt. Find your username in there and delete it. Save and close. Log into your server.
